Package: xdg-desktop-portal-gtk
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: A backend implementation for xdg-desktop-portal that is using GTK+.
 .
 This package contains the binary xdg-desktop-portal-gtk owning the D-Bus name
 org.freedesktop.impl.portal.desktop.gtk, which is the GTK+ backend to the implementation
 of the different desktop portals implemented by flatpak, so that sandboxed
 applications can access certain services from the host machine.
 .
 Besides, it also contains the definition of the different interfaces that
 will be implemented by both the frontend and the backends of those portals.
